{"tid":677270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺而家好多戇鳩仔係咪都撚狗撚狗以為自己好撚醒","createTime":"2018-05-25T05:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T07:30:23.000Z","uid":76115,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b20845da442767c7e2f4529163ec178fea3e3d","tid":677270,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"上次食茶記見到個後生仔同個friend傾政治<br />\n兩個都係講啲阿媽係女人咁嘅野, 咩民主唔係萬能, 權力要有制衡呢啲中學通識書真理<br />\n本來都無乜野, 點知佢個friend走左無耐, 就聽到個男仔講電話, 啱先同XXX傾, 撚左佢半個鐘, 唉我都唔想成日撚狗架...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我一聽真係打撚左個冷震, 正常人聽佢兩個講咁耐都唔會覺得佢地有咩高下分到出來, 但原來佢覺得自己一路撚緊狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家真係好多戇鳩仔上連登上壞腦, 成日話撚呢個撚個個, 以為自己識講少少反話, 講野大聲少少就係撚緊狗, 揸住一個撚字就覺得全世界無人醒得過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a23647166dab40a5e2414a1335cb5eec17e6067","tid":677270,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"單憑幾句表面野就話人戇鳩仔 你就好撚醒？"},{"pid":"300ba50985178e6af0af1d8cda2eddf378095c79","tid":677270,"uid":85612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"識少少扮代表再自稱撚狗嘅真心柒"},{"pid":"1c49fe0f1df475185d27083d3a038d9b4c8cf6ca","tid":677270,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>識少少扮代表再自稱撚狗</strong>嘅真心柒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係"},{"pid":"c4e820bc6d4d4f3fa51406923d4ea016d7e43c4f","tid":677270,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c49fe0f1df475185d27083d3a038d9b4c8cf6ca","tid":677270,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>識少少扮代表再自稱撚狗</strong>嘅真心柒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/n